    "text": "Goodbye, pals!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.854,
    "endTime": 147.68900000000002,
    "text": "-You brought homework? -No, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.731,
    "endTime": 157.198,
    "text": "It's a brochure detailing all the fun to be had at our final destination, the Great Barrier Reef! See, there's a huge assortment of slides and trampolines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.282,
    "endTime": 160.03500000000003,
    "text": "-And forts. -And ropes to swing on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.118,
    "endTime": 162.954,
    "text": "-And forts. -And a water park!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.038,
    "endTime": 165.04000000000002,
    "text": "Oh no, that's just where you drooled on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.376,
    "endTime": 169.92000000000002,
    "text": "-Goodbye, Patrick. -Goodbye, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.856,
    "endTime": 190.899,
    "text": "It's over. You can get out now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.983,
